Class XMLTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • Objects.XMLTag

  • public class XMLTag
extends java.lang.Object
    XMLTag POJO class. This is the generic class for all tags, specifying methods to initialize name, type, tag, value for them.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Vedika Ghei, Soha Parasnis, Tanisha Rathi, Vidushi Mishra
    See Also:
    EnumTag, EnumType, KMIPType
